---
import { SITE } from '../consts';
import SubscribeBox from './SubscribeBox.astro';
import PodcastLinks from './PodcastLinks.astro';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="wrap">
    <!-- 브랜드 매니페스토 + 뉴스레터 -->
    <div class="foot-top">
      <div class="foot-brand">
        <a class="foot-logo" href="/" aria-label="Crama 홈">Crama<span class="foot-logo__dot">.</span></a>
        <p class="foot-mani">트렌드를 <strong>먼저</strong> 읽는 사람들. 부의 격차는 돈이 아니라 <strong>정보의 시차</strong>에서 시작됩니다. 크라마는 그 시차를 0으로 좁힙니다.</p>
        <div class="foot-pod"><PodcastLinks /></div>
        <a class="foot-jocohunt" href="https://jocohunt.com/p/tu87yztf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="조코헌트 주간 1위 — 자세히 보기">
          <img src="https://jocohunt.com/images/badges/top1-light.svg" alt="Weekly #1 on jocoHunt" width="195" height="44" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="foot-news">
        <SubscribeBox />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 링크 컬럼 -->
    <nav class="foot-cols" aria-label="푸터 메뉴">
      <div class="foot-col">
        <h3>둘러보기</h3>
        <a href="/column/">칼럼</a>
        <a href="/guides/">가이드</a>
        <a href="/tools/">금융 계산기</a>
        <a href="/glossary/">용어사전</a>
      </div>
      <div class="foot-col">
        <h3>주제</h3>
        <a href="/category/money/">주식·재테크</a>
        <a href="/category/ai/">AI 트렌드</a>
        <a href="/category/income/">부업·지원금</a>
      </div>
      <div class="foot-col">
        <h3>크라마</h3>
        <a href="/about/">소개</a>
        <a href="/contact/">문의하기</a>
        <a href="/contact/">제휴·광고</a>
      </div>
      <div class="foot-col">
        <h3>정책</h3>
        <a href="/privacy/">개인정보처리방침</a>
        <a href="/terms/">이용약관</a>
        <a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 하단 바 -->
    <div class="foot-bottom">
      <div class="foot-copy">© {year} {SITE.name}. {SITE.tagline}.</div>
      <p class="foot-disc">콘텐츠는 정보 제공을 목적으로 하며 특정 상품·종목의 매매를 권유하지 않습니다. 투자 등 최종 판단과 책임은 이용자 본인에게 있습니다. · 문의 <a href="mailto:gmlthd94@gmail.com">gmlthd94@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style is:global>
  footer.site-footer {
    margin-top: 5rem; border-top: none;
    background: #15120e; color: #cfc8bd; font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding-block: 3.4rem 2rem; position: relative;
  }
  footer.site-footer::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: var(--accent);
  }

  /* 상단: 브랜드 / 뉴스레터 */
  .site-footer .foot-top {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 1fr; gap: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2.6rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
  }
  .site-footer .foot-brand { max-width: 30rem; }
  .site-footer .foot-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 2.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; line-height: 1;
  }
  .site-footer .foot-logo__dot { color: var(--accent); }
  .site-footer .foot-mani { margin: 0.85rem 0 1.4rem; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .site-footer .foot-mani strong { color: #e8a184; font-weight: 600; }
  .site-footer .foot-pod { margin-top: 0.2rem; }
  .site-footer .foot-jocohunt { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; opacity: .92; transition: opacity .15s; }
  .site-footer .foot-jocohunt:hover { opacity: 1; }
  .site-footer .foot-jocohunt img { height: 40px; width: auto; display: block; }

  /* 링크 4컬럼 */
  .site-footer .foot-cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2rem; padding: 2.5rem 0; }
  .site-footer .foot-col h3 {
    font-size: 0.74rem; letter-spacing: 0.09em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38); margin: 0 0 0.85rem; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .site-footer .foot-col a {
    display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.32rem 0; font-size: 0.92rem; transition: color .15s, transform .15s;
  }
  .site-footer .foot-col a:hover { color: #fff; transform: translateX(2px); }

  /* 하단 바 */
  .site-footer .foot-bottom {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.8rem 2rem; padding-top: 1.9rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
  }
  .site-footer .foot-copy { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .site-footer .foot-disc { margin: 0; max-width: 47rem; font-size: 0.78rem; line-height: 1.6; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.42); }
  .site-footer .foot-disc a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
  .site-footer .foot-disc a:hover { color: #e8a184; }

  /* 뉴스레터 박스 다크 보정 + 푸터 안에서는 단일 컬럼(2단 그리드의 칸 눌림·알약 줄바꿈 방지) */
  .site-footer .subscribe {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.5rem 1.6rem;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0; align-items: stretch;
  }
  .site-footer .subscribe__contact { white-space: nowrap; align-self: start; }
  .site-footer .subscribe__title { color: #fff; }
  .site-footer .subscribe__sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.58); }
  .site-footer .subscribe__contact { background: transparent; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.24); }
  .site-footer .subscribe__contact:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #e8a184; border-color: #e8a184; }
  .site-footer .subscribe__row input[type='email'] {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18); color: #fff;
  }
  .site-footer .subscribe__row input[type='email']::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }

  /* 팟캐스트 라벨 다크 보정 */
  .site-footer .podlinks__label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.58); }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .site-footer .foot-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.2rem; }
    .site-footer .foot-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.8rem 1.5rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    footer.site-footer { padding-block: 2.6rem 1.6rem; }
    .site-footer .foot-bottom { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
